  <description>
    <p>ABOUT APPLICATION :</p>
    <p>ConvertPanda aka Panda Video Converter is a powerful yet easy-to-use video converter that supports all major formats including MP4, MKV, MOV, AVI, MP3, and more.</p>
    <p>FEATURES :</p>
     <ul>
        <li>Convert all major video and audio formats with lossless compression.</li>
        <li>Extract crystal-clear HD audio from any video file.</li>
        <li>Customize video quality, resolution, and frame rate (FPS) with ease.</li>
        <li>Full support for surround sound systems (5.1 and 7.1 channels).</li>
        <li>Accelerate conversions using GPU-powered hardware acceleration.</li>
        <li>Batch process multiple files simultaneously for maximum efficiency.</li>
        <li>Quickly add files with simple drag-and-drop functionality.</li>
        <li>Monitor CPU performance in real time during conversions.</li>
        <li>Extensive codec support: H.264, HEVC, VP9, AAC, MP3, FLAC, and more.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>WHY CHOOSE CONVERTPANDA?</p>
        <ul>
            <li>User-friendly interface designed for smooth, hassle-free conversions.</li>
            <li>Lightning-fast performance with advanced GPU acceleration technology.</li>
            <li>Supports up to 8K video resolution and all major file formats.</li>
        </ul>
  </description>
